Lord Vishnu's Dasavataras on a limited access forum on Facebook. A learned =
friend wrote that "Krshna is the God-man", "Previous Avatars are a build-up=
 to this stage" and "Buddha after Krshna is like going back from the linear=
 progression of spirituality that the Avatars manifest one after the other =
upto Krshna".
=C2=A0
I want to emphatically disagree with this notion that =
Dasavatars of a "linear progression of spirituality..upto Krshna".
