y the qualities of soul may like the story that demonstrates how soul opera=
tes; one who is fascinated by the qualities of mind may like the story that=
 demonstrates how mind operates, and one who is fascinated by the qualities=
 of wisdom may like the story that
 demonstrates how wisdom operates. And s=
o on. But this is just a matter of taste and subjective preference.
=C2=A0
